-------------------------------------------------------------------
README  : Digital Signal Timing Diagram Ruby Library
Version : 1.0
Author  : Mark Fabbro
Date    : 2011/04/09
 
-------------------------------------------------------------------
  Description:
-------------------------------------------------------------------
A ruby library which allows the user to create simple digital signal 
timing diagrams.


-------------------------------------------------------------------
  Installation:
-------------------------------------------------------------------
1. Install ImageMagick Library
2. Install the rmagick ruby gem

OSX specific installation:
1. Install Xcode: 
		Can be found on the installation disk that shipped with 
		your Mac or downloaded from the apple website. 

2. Install ImageMagick library and its dependencies:
		git clone https://github.com/maddox/magick-installer.git
		sh ./magick-installer/magick-installer.sh

3. Install rmagick rubygem:
		sudo gem install rmagick


-------------------------------------------------------------------
  Library Use:
-------------------------------------------------------------------
See example.rb and exoutput.jpg


